      "line": 59,
      "message": "@Fiachra in this review https://gerrit.onap.org/r/c/oom/+/104168 made me think about one thing:\n\nif there's a CrashLoopBackoff and we restart the main container, as mycreds.prop is empty, we won't be able to restart it no?\n\n@krzysztof, @christophe, any thoughts?",
