      "patchset_number": 21,
      "line": 59,
      "message": "mmmh yes I see what you mean in that case, there is a risk.\nMaybe that cat /dev/null is too much; it would have been be nice to decode passwords only when needed, or maybe have an elegant way to ask k8s to rerun the init containers (or some of them) when main container(s) fail. \nIn fact, I've found that others are asking for this : https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/issues/52345",
      "author": {
